OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1778191867
OL,3,CYorkshire Labour MPs brace for painful
OL,4,Clocal election results
OL,6,FIf you ask Labour MPs in the Calendar
OL,7,Fregion how the local elections will
OL,8,Fgo, the response isn't exactly
OL,9,Fpositive.
OL,11,FIt's a "giant tombola of
OL,12,Fdissatisfaction," says one.
OL,14,FAnother tells me: "Where we have
OL,15,Felections is worst, where we don't is
OL,16,Fbest."
OL,18,FAnd just one more for good measure:
OL,19,F"If it's a disaster, it will be better
OL,20,Fthan expected."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1778191867
OL,3,CYorkshire Labour MPs brace for painful
OL,4,Clocal election results
OL,6,FThey don't want to have their names
OL,7,Fattached to their comments, but the
OL,8,Fgeneral mood among Labour MPs about
OL,9,Fthese elections is dismal.
OL,11,FOne of the party's biggest concerns is
OL,12,FBarnsley Council, which has been
OL,13,Fremarkably stable in a time of
OL,14,Fpolitical turbulence.
OL,16,FLabour has held control since 1974,
OL,17,Fand leader Sir Stephen Houghton has
OL,18,Fbeen in post since 1996, since when
OL,19,Fnine Prime Ministers have served in
OL,20,FNumber 10.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1778191867
OL,3,CYorkshire Labour MPs brace for painful
OL,4,Clocal election results
OL,6,FBut could that all be about to change
OL,7,Fin a rare all-out election where every
OL,8,Fseat is up for grabs?
OL,10,FThat's the fear for the party with
OL,11,Fsenior Reform sources increasingly
OL,12,Fconfident about taking the council.
OL,14,FOne source says Labour is "underwater"
OL,15,Fthere.
OL,17,FOthers on the ground are less
OL,18,Fpessimistic, saying that support for
OL,19,Fthe party at a local level may help
OL,20,FLabour hold onto voters who have
OL,21,Fturned away from them nationally.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1778191867
OL,3,CYorkshire Labour MPs brace for painful
OL,4,Clocal election results
OL,6,FBut an opinion piece looking at where
OL,7,FLabour politicians feel optimistic
OL,8,Fwould be brief.
OL,10,FAcross the region, they are preparing
OL,11,Ffor bad result after bad result as
OL,12,Fcounting begins overnight and
OL,13,Fcontinues through Friday and, in
OL,14,FBradford, Saturday.
OL,16,FIn some places the challenge comes
OL,17,Fpredominantly from Reform.
OL,19,FIn others, like Sheffield, the Greens,
OL,20,Fthe Liberal Democrats and Independents
OL,21,Fare also hoping to challenge Labour.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1778191867
OL,3,CYorkshire Labour MPs brace for painful
OL,4,Clocal election results
OL,6,FOn the doorstep, people repeatedly
OL,7,Fexpress frustration with the
OL,8,Fgovernment and specifically with Keir
OL,9,FStarmer, I am told.
OL,11,FThat is usual for a local election,
OL,12,Fbut with the rise of challenger
OL,13,Fparties on the left and right, people
OL,14,Fnow feel they have real alternatives
OL,15,Fto channel that dissatisfaction.
OL,17,FNow that's not to say Labour is alone
OL,18,Fin facing a difficult night in the
OL,19,Fregion.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
